title: The One About 2021
description:
On the last episode of Sibling Rivalry of the year, Bob and Monét reflect on 2021! The two talk Raven Symone's Oprah interview, DJ-ing, Monét's love for Chelsea Handler, and Nicole Byer's killer year. Tune in to hear how they celebrated Christmas, their highlight's of 2021 and their hopes for 2022.
